value.title: NEAR Events
value.description:
About Event

​The future of AI won’t be centralized. It will be Private. Intelligent. Yours.

​This February, NEARCON lands in San Francisco, the epicenter of AI and tech. Two days of keynotes, debates, and demos that cut through the hype and show what’s real.

​Join founders, researchers, and builders shaping the AI Economy and the next generation of decentralized AI infrastructure. Expect:

​Visionary keynotes from global AI and blockchain pioneers

​Live agent demos and hands-on workshops

​D
